  "texts": [
    "In the simplest version, they replay each trajectory with the goal achieved in the final state of the episode.",
    "However, they have experimentally evaluated different types and quantities of additional goals.",
    "In all cases, they also replay each trajectory with the original goal.",
    "The authors argue that one can see HER as a form of implicit curriculum because the goals used for replay naturally shift from simple to achieve even by a random agent to more difficult ones.",
    "However, HER does not require having any control over the distribution of initial environment states."
  ],
